    <Folder>
      <name>餐廳推薦</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Ver De El Nido 蔬食餐廳</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Sylvia&小編最愛<br>素食者不用說絕對愛爆<br>但他顛覆葷食者三觀，讓小編一週可以吃4次<br>午餐-優格碗-咖啡-晚餐通通都大推]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1592-E65100-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.389259,11.1802399,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Sunmai Sunset Restaurant</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Nacpan 最棒沙灘餐廳&酒吧<br>在這混整天都可以<br>披薩.豬肋排必吃]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1592-E65100-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.4222412,11.3129091,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Piece of Sky El Nido</name>
        <description><![CDATA[可以看著愛妮島鎮沙灘晚霞享用晚餐<br>高品質的菲式餐酒館<br>魚排,脆皮豬排,pork sisi必點]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1592-E65100-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3894111,11.1799674,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Oceanview Chinese Restaurant (望海楼中式餐厅)</name>
        <description>深深行程團第一天晚餐</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1592-E65100-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3891563,11.1800613,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Lechon Co by H Hospitality Group</name>
        <description>大節日才能吃到的脆皮烤乳豬，現在這裡也可以吃到摟！</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1592-E65100-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3893787,11.1800086,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Big Bad Thai 泰式</name>
        <description><![CDATA[最好吃泰式無誤（畢竟只有一家）<br>但真的很好吃拉！<br>旺季需要訂位非常熱門的一家餐廳]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3910627,11.1812555,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>The Food Truck 泰式</name>
        <description>也好吃又可愛的卡車餐車</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3916427,11.1814287,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Not so Thai 越+泰</name>
        <description>越南＋泰國餐廳</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3903962,11.1775069,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[Altrov'e Express Pizza]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[之前最有名的pizza店搬家到這裡喔！<br>松露披薩.燉飯必吃！！<br>現在有兩間分店喔！（在對面而以）]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3912897,11.1811226,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>BASIL Pizza Elnido</name>
        <description><![CDATA[原本最有名pizza原址開另一家pizza<br>也好吃但小編覺得偏油<br>然後要脫鞋（？]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3915491,11.1814198,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[Gorgonzola Pizza & Pasta - El Nido]]></name>
        <description>素食超大披薩</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3917498,11.1816328,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Angel Wish 海鮮</name>
        <description><![CDATA[當地海鮮菲式餐廳，門口直接挑選新鮮海鮮<br>重口味.海鮮沒問題！<br>但腸胃敏感者建議還是不要嘗試海鮮]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3889593,11.1804056,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Haim Chicken Restaurant</name>
        <description>菲律賓連鎖快餐店，著名烤雞飯好吃！</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3891491,11.179931,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[Maa's Grill 菲律賓料理]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[便宜好吃的菲律賓當地料理<br>他的咖哩很好吃！]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.389755,11.1803474,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Inasal Eats Co. El Nido 菲律賓料理</name>
        <description><![CDATA[菲律賓當地烤肉飯餐廳<br>算難得乾淨的一間<br>蠻推薦可以來體驗手抓飯喔！（還是可以用餐具）]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3912676,11.1810502,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>El Nido Boutique Artcafe</name>
        <description><![CDATA[有自己農場的老字號餐廳<br>西式餐點跟菲餐都還不錯]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3879394,11.1801397,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>I.B.R restaurant 菲律賓料理</name>
        <description><![CDATA[如果想試試菲律賓當地料理<br>可以來試試看....<br>安全能吃，但不保證好吃好哈哈<br>深深只吃他們家的LOMI，酒後好食]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3906964,11.1807472,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Happiness Beach Bar</name>
        <description>總是人超多的異國餐廳</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3883365,11.18018,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>DRYFT Fish OOPA 韓式</name>
        <description>韓式餐廳，都好吃！！</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3903539,11.180601,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Biryani Kitchen 印度料理</name>
        <description><![CDATA[印度炒飯份量大又好吃<br>印度餅配咖哩也很讚<br>但咖哩口味很異國，自行斟酌]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3903938,11.1804405,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Osaka Castle 日式</name>
        <description><![CDATA[日本人開的日式料理～<br>丼飯跟章魚燒可吃！]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            119.3911956,11.1813067,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[McDonald's]]></name>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-0288D1-labelson-nodesc</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
